name: Ghislaine (Mushoku Tensei)
description:
It is a character LoRA of Ghislaine from Mushoku Tensei: Jobless Reincarnation. V1.0 was trained on AbyssOrangeMix2_hard model. V1.1 was trained on NovelAI.

Recommend add "one-eyed, grey hair, cat ears," for bertter appearance, "red bandeau, green pants, fur coat" for clothes

modelVersions.name: v1.1
modelVersions.description: Retrained the model with doubled dataset on NovelAI model following this guide: https://civitai.com/models/22530/guide-make-your-own-loras-easy-and-free
